Class ChatroomToChatroomAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • yn4_jjc7.client.model.chatroom.ChatroomToChatroomAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    common.chatroom.IChatroomToChatroomAdapter, java.io.Serializable

    public class ChatroomToChatroomAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements common.chatroom.IChatroomToChatroomAdapter
    Concrete implementation of a chatroom to chatroom adapter. This is used to communicate from one chatroom to another over a remote interface.
    Author:
    Jayson Carter, Sean Harger
